1
00:00:01,333 --> 00:00:04,266
[LELEI] A Gate connecting to
another world appeared in Japan.

2
00:00:04,366 --> 00:00:06,600
After fighting back the army
that came through it,

3
00:00:06,700 --> 00:00:09,800
the Self‐Defense Force was sent
to the other side.

4
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:13,733
[LELEI] Itami was put in charge
of the 3rd Deep Reconnaissance
and Surveillance Unit.

5
00:00:13,833 --> 00:00:16,333
The group witnesses a flame
dragon attacking a settlement.

6
00:00:16,433 --> 00:00:20,766
[LELEI] There, they discover a
girl, the sole survivor of the
attack.

7
00:00:21,733 --> 00:00:23,400
[YOJI] (grunts)

8
00:00:29,933 --> 00:00:32,100
[YOJI] Got her!

9
00:00:32,200 --> 00:00:35,400
[KUWABARA] Easy, you guys!
Steady, steady...

10
00:00:41,200 --> 00:00:43,033
[YOJI] We found a person! Hurry
up!

11
00:00:43,133 --> 00:00:44,333
[ALL] Roger.

12
00:00:44,433 --> 00:00:46,200
[YOJI] Eh?

13
00:00:46,933 --> 00:00:51,633
I guess not exactly a person.

14
00:02:26,745 --> 00:02:27,873
[MARI] Her BPs high
enough to move her!

15
00:02:27,973 --> 00:02:30,873
But we gotta get her out of
these wet clothes!

16
00:02:30,973 --> 00:02:31,973
[SHINO] Sorry, but this has
gotta go.

17
00:02:34,807 --> 00:02:36,007
[KURATA] (happy) An elf!

18
00:02:36,107 --> 00:02:38,140
And not just any elf. A blonde
elf too!

19
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,507
[KURATA] Now that's the kinda
thing

20
00:02:39,607 --> 00:02:42,073
I was expecting to find out
here!

21
00:02:42,173 --> 00:02:43,673
[KURATA] (giggles) We hit the
jackpot this time baby!

22
00:02:43,773 --> 00:02:45,907
[YOJI] OK... you're into elves?

23
00:02:46,007 --> 00:02:48,040
[MARI] Excuse me, sir.

24
00:02:48,140 --> 00:02:49,273
[YOJI] So, how's she doing?

25
00:02:49,373 --> 00:02:51,007
[MARI] Her temp's back down to
normal...

26
00:02:51,107 --> 00:02:52,940
She's no longer in critical
condition.

27
00:02:53,040 --> 00:02:54,973
[YOJI] That's good to hear.

28
00:02:55,073 --> 00:02:57,873
[MARI] All right... so how would
you like to proceed?

29
00:02:57,973 --> 00:03:00,040
[YOJI] Let's see...

30
00:03:00,140 --> 00:03:03,173
A dry pair of boots'd be pretty
kick ass right about now!

31
00:03:03,273 --> 00:03:04,273
[MARI] What?

32
00:03:04,373 --> 00:03:06,973
Never mind. no way we
can leave her here...

33
00:03:07,073 --> 00:03:09,507
she ended up losing her entire
village.

34
00:03:09,607 --> 00:03:12,107
We'll classify her as a refugee
and take her with us.

35
00:03:12,207 --> 00:03:14,073
[MARI] Now why did I get the
feeling you were gonna

36
00:03:14,173 --> 00:03:16,907
come up with something like that
Lieutenant?

37
00:03:17,007 --> 00:03:18,773
[YOJI] Eheh... pretty humane
of me don'tcha think?

38
00:03:18,873 --> 00:03:21,973
[MARI] Yeah...
wouldn't go that far.
[YOJI] Huh?

39
00:03:22,073 --> 00:03:23,707
[MARI] I mean, I was thinking
you might've done it

40
00:03:23,807 --> 00:03:24,973
because she was an elf...

41
00:03:25,073 --> 00:03:27,507
Knowing what you do in your
spare time...

42
00:03:27,607 --> 00:03:31,207
it'd be pretty rude of me to
point out now wouldn't it sir?

43
00:03:37,507 --> 00:03:40,007
[YOJI] That's it.
We should head back to Camp
Alnus.

44
00:03:40,107 --> 00:03:43,273
It'll be best to take the road
through Coda Village.

45
00:03:43,373 --> 00:03:45,307
[KURATA] You know what,
Lieutenant...

46
00:03:45,407 --> 00:03:47,307
[KURATA] I'm thinking we'll
probably run into

47
00:03:47,407 --> 00:03:49,940
a dragon again before a
cat‐girl, huh?

48
00:03:50,040 --> 00:03:52,073
[YOJI] Better watch what you
say,.

49
00:03:52,173 --> 00:03:54,473
Or else it might come true,
you know.

50
00:03:56,507 --> 00:03:57,707
[VILLAGE CHIEF] Dear God!

51
