[YOJI] Malu haluu. Uh, Big bird.

53
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:05,707
[YOJI] Lahoo. Forest. On fire.

54
00:04:05,807 --> 00:04:07,440
[VILLAGE CHIEF] Flame dragon!

55
00:04:07,540 --> 00:04:08,440
[VILLAGER] (slow gasp) No way...

56
00:04:08,540 --> 00:04:09,573
[VILLAGER ] Unbelievable...

57
00:04:09,673 --> 00:04:11,707
[YOJI] Mlapalaa, shooting
fire...

58
00:04:11,807 --> 00:04:13,573
Pabla maloo burned to death.

59
00:04:14,773 --> 00:04:18,273
[YOJI] And one girl. We saved...
Yarimila?

60
00:04:18,373 --> 00:04:19,373
[VILLAGE CHIEF] Oh?

61
00:04:19,473 --> 00:04:21,573
And she's the only survivor?

62
00:04:21,673 --> 00:04:23,007
That is just awful.

63
00:04:23,107 --> 00:04:24,807
[YOJI] Kalahoo. Can you help?

64
00:04:24,907 --> 00:04:28,907
[VILLAGE CHIEF] Mm‐mmm...
We can't care for an elf.

65
00:04:29,007 --> 00:04:30,673
And besides, we need to find a
way

66
00:04:30,773 --> 00:04:32,973
to get out of here ourselves.

67
00:04:33,073 --> 00:04:34,940
[YOJI] Onaha... You leave?

68
00:04:35,040 --> 00:04:36,573
[VILLAGE CHIEF] Yes...

69
00:04:36,673 --> 00:04:38,373
Once a Flame dragon gets a taste

70
00:04:38,473 --> 00:04:41,873
of human or elven flesh
it will be back for more.

71
00:04:44,673 --> 00:04:45,907
[MELIZA] (grunt) Come on! We
gotta go!

72
00:04:46,007 --> 00:04:47,240
[HUSBAND and SON] Got it!

73
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:48,273
[MELIZA] Right!

74
