[KATO] (grunts and groans)

75
00:05:06,073 --> 00:05:08,373
[KATO] Ahhhhhhhhhh!

76
00:05:08,473 --> 00:05:11,340
[LELEI] Um Master we can't load
anything else on the cart.

77
00:05:11,440 --> 00:05:14,907
Lelei...! I need to take my
books with me! Hear me?

78
00:05:15,007 --> 00:05:17,340
[KATO] Lelei... we've got to
come up with something.

79
00:05:17,973 --> 00:05:19,140
[LELEI] Certainly...

80
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,873
The books that have spells
and incantations

81
