should be given
the highest value.

82
00:05:22,473 --> 00:05:25,540
[KATO] That's right! You really
are a genius, aren't you?

83
00:05:25,640 --> 00:05:29,607
[KATO] why is there dragon here
anyway? Most peculiar.

